RACE.RACE_TEXT: RUIDOSO DOWNS RACE 2 5 1/2F Dirt CR: 54. Trial Purse 8000. FOR TWO YEAR OLD FILLIES REGISTERED NEW MEXICO BREDS THAT WERE NOMINATED AND REMAIN ELIGIBLE TO THE 2023 RIO GRANDE SENORITA FUTURITY. All horses must enter for the trial on Friday, July 14, 2023 by 11:00 A.M. and pay $800 entry fee. Qualifiers will be d etermined by order of finish, ten horse gate for the finals. Late nominations of $10,000 will be accepted at time of entry and includes all fees into the trials. Weight: 120 lbs.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: MAKE UP A STORY dropped inside to save ground mid pack, angled out into the turn, bid four wide, closed steadily and wore down PAYINGOFFMYMARKER to get up late. PAYINGOFFMYMARKER set a pressured pace, inched away on the turn, led to the final strides and was outfinished. MARK IT DOWN bobbled after the start, stalked the pace, angled in for the drive, lacked the needed rally and settled for show. NOT TO FANCY came in and was steadied at the start, was taken wide and fell far back, advanced to the turn and closed well. STORM IN THE VALLE pressed the pace along the inside to the turn and gave way. KENTUCKY GOLD raced five wide along the backstretch, showed speed to the turn and gave way. STREET MARK raced six wide along the backstretch, showed speed to the turn and gave way.
